---
title: Tahini Drizzled Chicken with Broccoli Rice
description: This ain't no ordinary rice bowl! Grate grate grate is all you need to do for rice made from broccoli. Topped with juicy pan-seared chicken and tahini drizzle, you won't regret trying something new!

